{
  "stem": "142.6",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't know, [INAUDIBLE] different things, the place of the body.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But we have to untangle everything.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We had to be powerful to get even-- if they were like this, together, you know, or [INAUDIBLE] were a few people.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We are not alone.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not too many.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "A few-- a few.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Four, five of them, I think.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Always were-- were people helping us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They want to get rid fast, put them to the ovens so that we can paint it and finish with it.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So maybe another transport was coming, you know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Maybe a-- we did a-- a cane, and a-- [INAUDIBLE] think, a strap or whatever.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But always [INAUDIBLE] things there to-- to work, and-- that [INAUDIBLE] take them to be ready to be-- to be go to the ovens.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Put the cane up in here, [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the-- well, it put it-- put it in a stretcher, whatever it was, you know, to take it to the elevator.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But we had a few people taking one or two at a time to the elevator.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I-- I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I think we were taking them out first.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And some, we didn't have to put in a stretcher.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We just move around to the elevator.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was not too far away.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not long.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was just a-- a few minutes.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Is that mine?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the only procedure is we take the bodies up to the elevator, to the second floor, and to the ovens.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And people are there doing their job, put-- putting-- we have nothing, anything to do when we are there.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they would put it in a stretcher, put it inside the oven, and get cremated.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
